t_error_ratio", "cpu_usage", "error_ratio", "node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes", "node_memory_usage_rate", "pod_cpu_usage", "rrt", "rrt_max"], "log_analysis_findings": "基于日志分析，我已经识别出故障的根本原因。以下是详细的分析结果：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\"gc\", \"GCHelper\", \"AdService--gc-1749705397\", \"DeadlineExceeded\", \"context deadline exceeded\", \"timeout\", \"Rule.execute\", \"byteman gc helper trigger gc\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"adservice 服务遭受了 GC (垃圾回收) 故障注入攻击，导致频繁的垃圾回收操作，表现为 AdService--gc 标签的规则被反复执行，总计 155 次 Rule.execute 调用\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Rule.execute called for AdService--gc-1749705397_40:0 (出现次数:155), byteman gc helper trigger gc, AdService--gc-1749705397 execute() (出现次数:155)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"adservice 的 Byteman 代理启动失败，导致服务无法正常处理请求，出现 Agent failed to start! 错误\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Agent failed to start! (出现次数:2), Caused by: java.lang.Exception: Main : attempting to load Byteman agent more than once (出现次数:2)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"frontend 服务调用 adservice 时出现超时错误，由于 adservice 的 GC 故障导致响应延迟，表现为 context deadline exceeded 错误\",\n      \"evidence\": \"failed to get ads: rpc error: code = DeadlineExceeded desc = context deadline exceeded (出现次数:3)\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**分析总结**：\n- **根因服务**：adservice\n- **故障类型**：GC (垃圾回收) 故障注入攻击\n- **影响范围**：adservice 自身服务异常，导致 frontend 服务调用超时\n- **关键证据**：AdService--gc 规则被触发了 155 次，Byteman 代理启动失败，frontend 出现超时错误\n\n这明显是一个由混沌工程工具（如 Chaos Mesh）注入的 GC 故障场景，导致 adservice 性能严重下降，进而影响整个系统的正常运行。", "trace_analysis_findings": "基于获取到的调用链数据，我已经完成了对故障期间的系统扫描分析。以下是详细的分析结果：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\n    \"rrt_max\",\n    \"error_ratio\",\n    \"checkoutservice->cartservice\",\n    \"checkoutservice->productcatalogservice\",\n    \"frontend->adservice\",\n    \"cartservice->redis\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"CartService\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"CartService的GetCart操作延迟显著增加：正常平均2556ms，异常时达到25489ms（延迟倍数10倍）；CartService-2实例延迟从1952ms增至33235ms（延迟倍数17倍）\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"Redis\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Redis HGET操作延迟异常：cartservice-1调用的Redis从1771ms增至16780ms（延迟倍数9.5倍）；cartservice-2调用的Redis从1553ms增至8005ms（延迟倍数5.2倍）\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"ProductCatalogService\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"ProductCatalogService的GetProduct操作延迟增加：从正常10474ms增至18274ms（延迟倍数1.7倍），多个实例均受影响\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"AdService\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"AdService出现'context deadline exceeded'错误，frontend调用AdService时发生超时错误，导致前端服务异常\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"EmailService\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"EmailService的SendOrderConfirmation操作延迟增加：从正常669ms增至1319ms（延迟倍数2倍），多个实例受影响\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n## 关键发现总结：\n\n1. **最严重的延迟问题**：CartService及其依赖的Redis服务出现严重延迟，延迟倍数高达10-17倍，表明这是系统的主要瓶颈。\n\n2. **错误传播路径**：Redis延迟 → CartService延迟 → CheckoutService延迟 → 前端服务异常。\n\n3. **关键错误**：AdService出现超时错误（context deadline exceeded），这可能与下游依赖的数据库或网络问题有关。\n\n4. **影响范围**：故障影响了整个购物流程，包括购物车、产品目录、邮件服务等多个核心组件。\n\n**建议下一步**：深入分析Redis和AdService的底层依赖，特别是TiDB数据库的连接状态和网络状况，以确定根本原因。", "metric_analysis_findings": "Based on my analysis of the trace data during the fault period, I've identified several significant anomalies. Here's my comprehensive assessment:\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\"node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes\", \"node_memory_usage_rate\", \"cpu_usage\", \"rrt_max\", \"rrt\", \"pod_cpu_usage\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"aiops-k8s-08\",\n      \"reason\": \"Node memory availability significantly decreased with node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes showing 28.13% reduction (from 12.87GB to 9.70GB)\",\n      \"evidence\": \"node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes median dropped from 12,871,962,624 bytes to 9,697,898,496 bytes (28.13% decrease)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"tidb-tidb\",\n      \"reason\": \"TiDB database CPU usage increased by 45.33% with cpu_usage metric showing significant spike\",\n      \"evidence\": \"cpu_usage median increased from 0.29 to 0.46 (45.33% increase)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"aiops-k8s-04\",\n      \"reason\": \"Node memory usage rate decreased by 13.6% indicating potential memory pressure or reclamation\",\n      \"evidence\": \"node_memory_usage_rate median decreased from 39.33% to 34.32% (13.6% decrease)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend-1\",\n      \"reason\": \"Frontend service experienced significant response time degradation with rrt_max showing 36.1% P99 increase\",\n      \"evidence\": \"frontend-1 rrt_max P99 increased from 386,718.2 to 557,044.08 (36.1% increase)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"Checkout service response time increased with rrt_max showing 34.55% P99 degradation\",\n      \"evidence\": \"checkoutservice-0 rrt_max P99 increased from 348,932.96 to 494,662.76 (34.55% increase)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"paymentservice-1\",\n      \"reason\": \"Payment service response time degraded with rrt_max showing 33.73% median increase and 33.03% P99 increase\",\n      \"evidence\": \"paymentservice-1 rrt_max median increased from 2,889 to 4,061 (33.73% increase), P99 increased from 6,651.34 to 9,282.72 (33.03% increase)\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n## Key Findings Summary:\n\n1. **Node-Level Issue**: `aiops-k8s-08` shows significant memory pressure with available memory dropping by 28.13%. This node hosts critical services including `redis-cart-0`.\n\n2. **Database Performance**: `tidb-tidb` experienced 45.33% CPU usage increase, indicating potential database performance issues.\n\n3. **Service Degradation**: Multiple services show response time degradation:\n   - `frontend-1`: 36.1% P99 rrt_max increase\n   - `checkoutservice-0`: 34.55% P99 rrt_max increase  \n   - `paymentservice-1`: 33.73% median rrt_max increase\n\nThe memory pressure on `aiops-k8s-08` combined with TiDB CPU spike suggests a potential resource contention issue that cascaded to affect service performance across the system."}
